This directory contains some testing program of Hammersley and Halton
points. Note that subdirectories only contains the snapshot of the
source codes when I submitted the paper to Journal of Graphics Tools

Name       Description
====	   ===========
raytrace/  A ray tracer with supersampling. Implemented on Rayshade 4.0.6.
	   Enhanced 2.

sampexp/   Sample the surface exposure. Implemented on Rayshade 4.0.6
	   Enhanced 2.

udpoint/   An OpenGL program demo the appearance of Hammersley and Halton
	   points on sphere and plane.


T T